parameters.name: DeploymentSetId
parameters.description: The ID of the deployment set.

parameters.name: DeploymentSetName
parameters.description: The new name of the deployment set. The name must be 2 to 128 characters in length. It must start with a letter and cannot start with http:// or https://. It can contain letters, digits, colons (:), underscores (\_), and hyphens (-).

parameters.name: Description
parameters.description: The new description of the deployment set. The description must be 2 to 256 characters in length and cannot start with http:// or https://.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the deployment set. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
